reviewText: Playboy Sizzling Sex Stars is good DVD that I like it with HD pictures , a lot of Models are beautiful and so hot body ,

...featuring some of the sex industries best adult stars, from Jenna Jameson, Asia Carrera, Julia Ann, Brittany Andrews, Tera Patrick and many others, I got more than I bargained for in this dvd. I expected the usual tame playboy productions which never really 'show' anything...but I was pleasantly supprised...in this one you get to see everything as each girl talks openly about their lives in the industry and then enact some of their widest fantasies...some of the masturbation scenes do not seem simulated at all...plenty of vulva close ups, labia spreading...but no digital penetration...it was pretty cool...I wish playboy could make more dvd's like this...

This Playboy release reveals some girls who are better known as pornstars than as pin-ups. The girls I liked best were Tera Patrick and Jenna Jameson. Janine Lindemulder, who did some excellent work for Penthouse, was rather disappointing because of all the tatoos she nowadays has.
Each girl is first shown taking part in a photo session. After that the action gets a little more intimate and for Playboy standards quite revealing. In all, this DVD is a good buy for people who would like to see their favourite pornstars in a different light.
